{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u300cHydra Hyde Land\u300d is a deck-building rogue-lite game. The player must defeat a \u201ccertain demon\u201d in order to break the curse placed on the girl who saved his life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bc Story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">~ The Curse of Hydra Consuming a Young Girl ~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The main character was saved by a girl when he was fainting in the forest. The girl said that she and her friends were traveling in search of a \u201ccertain demon\u201d. Having saved his life, he decides to accompany the girl on her journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bcGame System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">~ Deck-building card battles ~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battles are played using cards. The game progresses on a turn-based system, and cards can be used by consuming \u201chand costs. New cards can be obtained by defeating enemies, and the player builds a deck with these cards to advance in the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">~ Events that occur in the dungeon ~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In dungeons, various events such as \u201cblacksmith events,\u201d \u201cstore events,\u201d and \u201cselective events\u201d occur at random. It is important to make good use of these events in order to advance in your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bc How to operate</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use mouse only.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736271727","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736271727","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/243ff8906ddf36d084f34eb18226ceb23bbee8ab/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736271727","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/243ff8906ddf36d084f34eb18226ceb23bbee8ab/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736271727","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u300cHydra Hyde Land\u300d is a deck-building rogue-lite game. The player must defeat a \u201ccertain demon\u201d in order to break the curse placed on the girl who saved his life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bc Story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">~ The Curse of Hydra Consuming a Young Girl ~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The main character was saved by a girl when he was fainting in the forest. The girl said that she and her friends were traveling in search of a \u201ccertain demon\u201d. Having saved his life, he decides to accompany the girl on her journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bcGame System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">~ Deck-building card battles ~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battles are played using cards. The game progresses on a turn-based system, and cards can be used by consuming \u201chand costs. New cards can be obtained by defeating enemies, and the player builds a deck with these cards to advance in the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">~ Events that occur in the dungeon ~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In dungeons, various events such as \u201cblacksmith events,\u201d \u201cstore events,\u201d and \u201cselective events\u201d occur at random. It is important to make good use of these events in order to advance in your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bc How to operate</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use mouse only.</p>","developers":["\u3059\u304f\u3048\u3042"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}]